data_preprocessed(data_file)[source]#

Read and preprocess data

Parameters:

data_file (str) – name of locally saved data file.

Returns:

  • df_joined (polars.DataFrame) – Preprocessed data set with 84 observations and 6 variables (subject, gender, scenario, attitude, frequency, mean_pitch).

  • summaries (polars.DataFrame) – Mean pitch value grouped by attitude (informel, polite) and gender (female, male).
